In a summary, the project roadmap includes: â†“ 

1. Initial Setup and Planning
   - Define project scope and objectives
   - Set up version control (GitHub repository)
   - Create a project timeline with milestones
2. User Interface Design
   - Design wireframes for the application
    - Choose a color scheme and typography
    - Develop a responsive layout for different devices
3. Core Functionality Development
   - Implement user input for income and expenses
    - Create budget calculation algorithms
    - Develop data storage solutions (local storage or database)
4. Additional Features
    - Add expense categorization and tracking
    - Implement visualizations (emoji-based responses)
    - Set up notifications and reminders for budget limits
5. Testing and Debugging
    - Conduct unit testing for individual components
    - Perform integration testing for overall functionality
    - Fix bugs and optimize performance